<solution>
<p><ul><li>6.9031465397116</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={350}{e}^{{{0.14}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{920}={350}{e}^{{{0.14}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{920}}{{350}}={e}^{{{0.14}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{920}}{{350}}\right)}}}={0.14}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{920}}{{350}}\right)}}}}{{0.14}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={6.9031465397116}</m></p>
</solution>
